text:
Well that left me feeling hungry.  But entertained. 

A most happy anniversary to IVE. I’ve worked in music/theater for some time and cannot recall more dedication and grace and passion in a popular group. The team has made some very unique and captivating artistic choices and present with dedication and style. They have spread IVE magic around the globe and left many DIVE in their wake. The fact that they are adorable is the cherry on top. Here’s a toast to 3 years of magic and to the next 3 and beyond. Love these girls. Now,…… I need a snack.      Signed; Uncle Dive.
